## 05 — QA Plan (Draft)

### Goal
- Provide an executable QA checklist that validates every doc-defined feature end-to-end.

### Smoke suite (critical)
- Auth: register/login/logout, email verify, password reset
- Feed: for-you/following, explore, search, categories
- Creator profile: posts, subscribe, tip, message
- PPV: unlock post, verify access, verify purchase history
- Wallet: topup checkout redirect, balance updates, transactions list
- Notifications: in-app list, web push opt-in + delivery (where applicable)

### Regression checklist per module
- Subscriptions & payments
- Content (posts, reels, stories)
- Messaging (including paid/PPV messages)
- Creator dashboard + earnings
- Creator payouts + transactions

